  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395190/extras/952445f76cb9fc8d02adbbd832e12e4d.avif?t=1770382215\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br>BLASK 2 is a unique puzzle game where you control the environment<br>in order to hit all the goal markers with lasers.<br>Each shape acts as a room made of mirrors. By combining <br>and rotating each shape, a player can control where the laser beam<br>points.<br><br>This is second installment of the franchise.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395190/extras/097b8932f77597fc6cd255a4c1645efc.avif?t=1770382215\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Features:<br>- Unique mechanic where you combine and rotate shapes to control laser beam reflections<br>- Each puzzle can be solved in multiple ways<br>- Two difficulty settings<br>- Relaxing soundtrack<br>- Many new mechanics compared to BLASK<br>- Colorfull calming backgrounds",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395190/extras/952445f76cb9fc8d02adbbd832e12e4d.avif?t=1770382215\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br>BLASK 2 is a unique puzzle game where you control the environment<br>in order to hit all the goal markers with lasers.<br>Each shape acts as a room made of mirrors. By combining <br>and rotating each shape, a player can control where the laser beam<br>points.<br><br>This is second installment of the franchise.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395190/extras/097b8932f77597fc6cd255a4c1645efc.avif?t=1770382215\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Features:<br>- Unique mechanic where you combine and rotate shapes to control laser beam reflections<br>- Each puzzle can be solved in multiple ways<br>- Two difficulty settings<br>- Relaxing soundtrack<br>- Many new mechanics compared to BLASK<br>- Colorfull calming backgrounds",
